nodes.text: Star Wars Jedi Master Magazine 4 is the fourth issue of Star Wars Jedi Master Magazine. It was published by Titan Magazines on May 17, 2016.

Extend your knowledge, practice the ways of the Force, and improve your skills and talents with Star Wars Jedi Master Magazine #4! You will learn about planets and battles, important warriors, alien species and famous Jedi Knights that made history in this galaxy!
